---
// This component displays client testimonials and is purely presentational.
---
<section id="testimonials" class="py-10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="content-plate">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-center section-header-glow">Trusted by Local Businesses</h2>
        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4 mb-12 text-center">
            Hear what our partners have to say about working with Innotec.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Testimonial Card 1 -->
            <div class="tech-card text-left">
                <p class="italic mb-4">"Innotec completely modernized our network and their 24/7 support is a lifesaver. Our downtime is practically zero now. They're a true partner in our success."</p>
                <p class="font-bold text-[var(--lightest-slate)]">Sarah Johnson</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-[var(--cyan)] font-mono">Operations Manager, Permian Oilfield Services</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial Card 2 -->
            <div class="tech-card text-left">
                <p class="italic mb-4">"The cybersecurity audit and training from Innotec were invaluable. We feel so much more secure knowing our client data is protected by local experts who are always just a phone call away."</p>
                <p class="font-bold text-[var(--lightest-slate)]">David Chen</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-[var(--cyan)] font-mono">Owner, Andrews Accounting Group</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial Card 3 -->
            <div class="tech-card text-left">
                <p class="italic mb-4">"Migrating to the cloud seemed like a daunting task, but the Innotec team made it seamless. Our team can now collaborate from anywhere, securely and efficiently. Highly recommend."</p>
                <p class="font-bold text-[var(--lightest-slate)]">Maria Rodriguez</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-[var(--cyan)] font-mono">Principal, Rodriguez Construction</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>